values:
A line... where you have to come to the conclusion... that your never going to find anyone thats right for you. or anything that will ever work out.

there is a line...that I cannot cross.

there is a beautiful thing... on the other side of the line...


that everyone can see... but I cannot...

that thing... is true love.

AJ.

I have come to the conclusion that I will always be alone...

That I am sure of... no matter what... I will never be truly happy... I am not destined too...


I have no idea where to go... I'm slipping slowly back into depression...

Fuck this life... havent said that in a long time...


AJ.

so its been forever since I was last on here... Actually I had forgot about it until Dani K brought it up today... i dont have time to post anything long or about my life just yet... but I will do it later tonight... I think I will enjoy returning back here. so long.

AJ.

lalala.... well... haven't really been on here that often as I said I would, but I have been on myspace.com alot... but yea... I still love you guys.  Anyways... there is alot of stress in my life, trying to get a freaking job, and trying to sort things out with the girl I love (Kenna). It is driving me crazy... so yea... I am driving now... and almost getting myself killed, while driving... lol, I am still learning so back off, lol. so anyways... thats it for now... maybe more later... dont know... my internet is crap at the moment... so I don't know. bye!


A.J.

about a year ago... at the end of last summer, I went for a walk, and didn't plan on coming back. since then, I have felt happy and not all that depressed... but for some reason, now I always think about that walk, and what really happened that night... and why I came back. do not worry, I am not suicidal... its just that I wonder.. and I think about things that most people would not... and I am dwelling on them, it does not seem healthy... but I cannot stop doing it... I dont even enjoy talking to people anymore... I just like to be alone... I have noticed something, I love to be in a group, but I hate to talk... I will be with someone... but I just enjoy the silence... I dont like to talk anymore, I dont like to tell people about myself. I wish I knew why... but yea... so thats my update... I will try to get on here more often, I am getting better at it.

well, its memorial day, and there is nothing to do, my girlfriend is doing homework at home, and I am here, SOMEWHAT working on my poetry packet... so yea. To answer Danielle's question, her name is Kenna... saurret... I think thats how the last name is spelled, and she is a freshmen.  so yea, lol, she is great, she makes me laugh and I am so happy! well, better half ass my way a bit more on this project, cya!

A.J.

OH MY GOD!! life has changed sooo much, I am reading my old posts, and wondering what the HELL I was thinking.  So yea, havent been on here all year, sorry guy's!! I am in a relationship now with a great girl named Kenna (sorry cant spell last name) and it is really doing well!!  I can't believe I got this lucky!  but yea, it has been too long since I have been on here last, I miss hanging out with Danielle, we had so much fun, we have been so busy... which reminds me... that damn poetry packet is due next week... time to work on that... so yea... not much has been up, working on keeping my damn grades up.  other than that I am having a good year, fun in TA'ing for Mr. Land and all that... now it is time for me to read up on everyones posts!

A.J.

well, I'm back, in a new year, and with a new girlfriend!!! thsi one sooo much better than the last, (which things got really bad with, and I mean REALLY).  so yea, tons of things have happened!! but... I don't know where to start, for one, I am deeply in love with my girlfriend, this is going so much better than I ever imagined!!!! I love this, and I am loving life again, hopefully someone is still on here to see this! lol.

A.J.

well I'm back!!! for a break of about two weeks, for some ODD reason, lol.  So yea, just hanging with Danielle for now, then at 6 I am going back to the fair to hang with Kate and our friend Corynne, who I met through Kate.  So yea, not much to say right now, ttyal later!!


A.J.

I love it!!so yea, love you all, but i especially love you Kate!!!

1. I'm actually very shy when it comes to my true feelings inside.

2. I may talk alot, but doesnt mean I know what I am saying.

3. I am always depressed, happy or not, its deep inside, its hard to get out, I hide it.

4. I may have had over 35 girlfriends, but I only dumped 3 of them.

5. I am always confused, even if I'm the one talking, even if I have done it many times before.

6. my grades are bad, like below 2.0 bad, yea, that bad

7. scissors are my worst enemy, most of the scars on my arm arent from my cat Milo, their from small cuts of the scissors, but that was months ago, they won't leave me in peace...

Well, the first day of summer school of the third week is today, and I am bored out of my mind of it... there are three reasons to go today, to get my permit, to pass math, and to see Kate. even though I will barely do all three of em, its hard to balance everything out. Last night my friend Mike saw that i was telling Kate i love her, and of course, the first thing out of his mouth was, "I don't think its love", and I said "well then what is it?", and he said "it's probably lust dude...", LUST?! i think hes finally lost it, but it scares me, that maybe my mind is playing tricks on me, but its not like I didnt enjoy being single, when I met Kate i wasn't looking for a girlfriend, but I went out with her cause whenever I was around her i had a strange feeling like never before, I have felt lust...this is not lust... but if it is, and my mind is making me think its love, then what if I hurt her? I couldnt live with that on my conscious.... I am so confused as to what to do, I am definitely not breaking up with Kate, guess I am just gonna have to talk it out with her...well I hope everyone has fun working or sitting around, or whatever they are doing, and have a nice day. cya all!!


A.J.

well, i got my much needed haircut!!lol. but now i feel bald... I look bald too...help!!  well Mikes over, and we went looking for jobs around town today, only got two application, everywhere else has computer applications, or is not hiring, or is looking for older people.*sigh* ok, well im gonna let mike on, cya later all!!


A.J.
(love you Kate!)

I just wanted to tell everyone happy 4th of July, I hope you all enjoyed the fireworks, or being with your families... I had fun just sitting in my room, ok well, cya everybody...


A.J.

just got off the phone with Kate, she sounds like shes having fun.  I'm jealous, I just get to sit here and do nothing, this is so lame... but it makes me happy knowing she is enjoying herself. I wish I could hang out with her so much, but her parents don't know about us, and with their feelings about dating, it's better it stays that way...  but nothing can keep me from loving her, and thats all that matters, well, im gonna find something to do, cya all later!

A.J.

man, I don't knwo whats happening, I have never been this happy before.  I think Kate slipped something into my soda, lol. this is the best thing that could of ever happened to me, and I can't keep it to myself!! I checked out our horoscopes, as you can tell, I posted them after all, that something that happened today was told in the horoscope!!  It's like we're supposed to be togethor. usually I am paranoid that a girl is gonna cheat on me or leave me, but not now, I feel that I can trust Kate absolutely. my music plays for a new reason, to enjoy my happiness instead of wish for it.  I love this, its soo awesome!!Cya all!


A.J.

Your mother could be on your mind today, Andrew. The energy of the day could be inspiring you to think more about your family. If you aren't close to your mother, maybe that is a relationship that needs some work. Think about what your mom needs right now, and see if you can build a bridge to a better friendship. It could be time to start from the present and move forward. (mine)

Relationships of all kinds are likely to be strengthened today by an increased level of understanding on your part, Kate. Your thinking is greatly enhanced today by feeling, so you'll be more apt than usual to identify with the needs and desires of those around you. As a result, acquaintances could become friends, and friendships could progress into bonds that could last for life. Romance also benefits because of intensified empathy. Enjoy! (my awesome girlfriend, Kate's)

this is awesome, its really accurate. I love this stuff.

well, its been a long time, but I'm back, hopefully.  well alot has happened, and i have learned alot, I am no longer suicidal, and i have been in really good moods lately.  i have  anew girlfriend, and she is awesome, i love her so much.

ok, to start it out, my depression is gone, it has been for about two weeks now.  the therapist i was seeing, Al Santos, is awesome, hes really smart and helped me alot, alot of the time i felt really stupid, but he showed me i wasnt.  i have been really happy lately, i rarely get mad, frustrated yes, but mad no,lol.

then there is my girlfriend Kate, we are perfect for each other, she is the best. i love her alot, we started out looking and smiling at each other in math, summer school. then we started talking, she wishes we talked sooner, so do I!!! lol, anyways, we went out to se spiderman 2 yesterday and had alot of fun.  I really like being with her, even if she did elbow me 5 times in the car lol, on accident though.

wells thats all i can think of for now!!

cya later all

A.J.

well, its the first wedsneday of summer, and I have to go to work today for my second day.  It's not really a professional job though, its with my friends father, but I get paid a good amount, and the work is hard.  But unfortanetely I am sitting here waiting for his father to come and pick me up, but no sign so far, hes actually an hour late so far, doing good... I guess I will sit here a bit longer.  While I sit I can think about whether something I did last night was a good idea or bad.

well I wanna start off with saying that I am I bit sorry for what I said last night, I do not regret what I did, but I couldve said it in a nicer manner, sorry, I am being mature, so I would hope everyone that responds to this will be too, please.  other than that, my day has been alright, i am passin my modern world history calls no matter what, and I am actually getting along with MR. Cooper, I wonder if he still thinks im on drugs?? lol.  I can't wait till I start my job this summer, well I think my parents are mad at me, so I'm gonna go.

saw this coming, Sara broke up with me! big surprise, I'm so mad at her, as she is probably mad at me, but I don't care.  Time to look for someone else! YAY!  oh well, other than that I'm doing fine... i went to the therapist today, and he is really cool, he said i am one of the most thought out kids every gone into that office.  I have thought of becoming a therapist,  and I will look into it deeply.

got nothing to say, except I have NO idea if Sara likes me or not.  when I walk into the room she just says hi and goes off to do her own thing, I mean thats fine and all, but I wouldnt even mind a hug!  and whne i tell her how much she means to me she just smiles and says thanks, and she says nothing back to me, Sara I would rather be telling you this alone, but I HAVE to get it out of my system, its driving me crazy.  Sorry if you don't like me posting it, but then again knowing you you won't really care...we really need to talk, but I have no idea when we can, I can't call you now cause your doing your concert. bye


A.J.

I hate knowing that I am hurting people, and other times I hurt people because they have hurt me, and its the only way I know to react, I wish i was a rock and never hurt or got hurt by people, unless I was used to hurt someone, but then again thats even worse...anyways, I have not even been ON livejournal for the past week, been to busy going to friends house, and they hanging over here, so sorry for all you that wanna know how I am doing, yeah right, like anyone wants to know that...so not much has been up, except my strees for finsihing Mr. Arnette's super essay, i did the presentation on Friday, I dont even know what sleep is anymore...oh well, enough right now, this is making me depressed...Cya


A.J.

well, the day I thought would never see came, i am up to date wiht all my homework, my projecyt is gonna be on time, an I am ACTUALLY gonna finish my English essay after all, only problem is that I have to do my oral presentation tomorrow. so now i have started procrastinating on my social stuff,  its hard to keep these things in order. well gtg ttyl.


A.J.

I just read on of my friends posts, and I realized that I complain WAY too much,  and I need to stop, I need to be stronger than I am now, if I wanna get ANYWHERE in life.  I know now I am afriad of what I am going to grow up into, and I need to change that NOW, and I can. by the way, Mr' Land got this bogus editorial from someone around Paso, and it completely wrong, it calls him a bad teacher, that he does not know how to teach.  I think that if anyone that disagrees they should write back to the editor of the tribune.

I got in a nother fight with my parents last night, big surprise! and today I have spent the whole day working on a project, I took a break to do chores although, but every so often I would stray off and check my email or say "hi" to a friend.  and that just happened to be the exact time that they walk in to check on me... I hate my life... and I am starting to hate them.  I just wish i could be a loner sometimes, not have to worry bout having friends.  I hate complaining to friends, it makes me feel like a nerd, and weak.  I hate it.  but everyone always ask's me whats wrong, and I don't like to shove them out of it, thats just not me.  but I wish people would not aks and just let me sit there in peace...  nothing looks right to me! WHAT IS WRONG WITH ME...I cherish my friends, but right now I wish i did not, I think this is my depression.  I think its cause I wish no one would miss me when I was gone, but i don't know why...blah...pssshhhh.  danielle is gonna dye her hair, probably shoulda let her say that, but I don't have any idea why...her hair was fine the way it was before.  but what place am I in to judge her... I'm the suicidal one, and as my step dad tells me, also the idiot of the family.  and he went to college so he MUST be right.  all hail Tom! yea fucking right... whats wrong with me... I am not sure if what I am writing is all my true feelings, but it is whats going through my head right now, and before you get mad at me and think I am being stupid, talk to me.

I'm messing around with my internet, because it is keeping me amused and my ind off of the stupid thing I did, I barely said anything on the phone with Danielle and Sara.  I wanted to help, i wanted to say something, but I just did not want to get to, and I have no idea why, maybe i'm not up to it tonight, I am pretty tired.  but the reason I brought up the internet, is cause now i have three different toolbars up atr the top, Yahoo,MSN, and the best, Google. and I have no idea why.

what I never have understood is why people shift the blame on me.  take Sara for instance, apparently I hurt her in some way....HOW I DO NOT KNOW, but I did, and now she is getting mad at me and telling me she has feelings, I KNOW YOUR HUMAN SARA, but you don't seem to act it.  how do I know if I have hurt you if you never show your feelings, or shoot me donw when I ask whats wrong, JUST TRYING TO HELP FOR CRYING OUT LOUD. anyways, if I even hurt you a bit, its no match for what you did to me.

anyways, I have had a strange week.  the story I wrote is two days this week, and I thought it was the best way to tell you all what happened.  but yes, I WAS GOING TO KILL MYSELF, and was on the verge of acting it out. oh yea, I wanna thank Mrs. Abernathy for bringing my backpack to the coucelors office!! *sigh* I have so much more, but i am to depressed to type right now.

I HATE EVERYTHING,  everyone I ever cared about, it is slipping away, people have said things that cannot be taken away, and they say without caring how I will feel after i hear it...  I realize that some people do not care if I am here or not and I understand, cause apparently I have made their life hell.  and if those people really want me gone, THEN JUST TELL ME.  I want to know, I do not wanna force my living on them.

he walks through the school, he walked to school with her that morning, but they barely talked, and he wished that he could have said more, he wished, but knew he di not have any more courage left.  he walked to his class, passing a girl that was in one of his classes, and he looked at her, she was very pretty, he was sure she would never think about suicide, but then he got to thinking that she might, he wondered how much people thought about suicide in this school, even if it was just once, it could almost be the whole school.  he walked into his class, his teacher, much shorter than him looked at him a wide grin on her face said "hello! how are you?" he faked a weak smile and said "alright" she gave him a worried look but as the bell rang she walked to the front of the class, and started to teach them, like she always had, and all he could do to keep his mind off of things was to listen to her, but then came a moment when he was glad he did, she started talking about her personel life,and he looked and listened in curiosity, she said that she wanted to go to law school, which he was also very interested in. when she finished they presented a project they worked on and finished the day before, he went up with his group and told the class what their project meant, saying as he had the loudest and deapest voice in the group.  he went back to his seat, and as the class started to get up and work on their projects he sat there, not really wanting to move, he had most of the project done anyways, and it was all at home, so why work on it here? but as he stood up finnally the teacher called his name, he looked past everyone and saw a lady next to his teacher smiling at him, he walked to her and she asked him to go with him, as he walked out of the classroom, he knew what it was for, "are you a councelor?" he asked and she replied "yes" he looked down and walked ot the counciling office, he said "I know what this is for, but I talked to someone about it last night, a girl i know" and she said "can I ask the name?" he told her the name and asked "shes the one who told you about me, huh?" "yep, shes in my office" he was both confused and a bit frustrated, as they walked into her office he looked down to see her in a chair, she looked at him and smiled fakely, her eyes showing she had been crying.  he smiled a bit back and walked to the chair next to her and sat down. the lady then sat at her desk and looked at them for a moment, as she explained why he was there he would glance at her every so often, but it looked like she was ignoring him, he was afriad he had made her mad, and he looked down ashamed.  she asked after a bit if she shou7ld leave them alone, and he said " that'd be cool" and she stood up and walked out. after the door shut he stood up and touched her arm, she stood up and hugged him immediately, all he could think of saying was "I'm sorry", and she kept asking why, and all he could answer her with was "cause this is my fault". they sat back down and the lady finally walked back in, they talked for awhile, but when they got to her problems he listened, and he just felt worse, he was causing her all this pain, and he knew it, and he knew he was screwing up her life, and it hurt him even more, he did not know what to do but sit there staring at the floor, glancing at he revery so often, but she would still not look at him. he sat there, wishing he knew what to do.

I still don't know what to do...

A.J.

sometimes I wonder, why do people claim how I feel?  They say how or who I love, when they have no idea, they say I do not love them, when they do not know, because they never cared to truly listen to me.  they never heard my voice quiver when I held them in my arms and told them how much I cared for them.  they never knew why I sat there in silence and whne they asked whats wrong I just said I don't know, because I knew that they hated fighting, and if i said what it was then they would get mad and it would lead to a fight.  but it was true that there was love for another, but it was only the love for a friend that understood everything about you, and you her.  nothing more, but after the relationship had ended, and there was no more hope, I realized that the one that understood me the most, and I her, was the best match I could think of, and the love progressed by itself, lonely, without another loving it back, but whne that love finally had enough courage to show itself, it was too late, and the pain now is almost unbearable, but the love for the friend is still more powerful, it wants the best for her, even though it looks at her through my eyes and wants to be closer to her, and it crys, even if on the surface it doesn't show, when she cries.  it feels so bad, and does not know how to make up for it.

A.J.

never again, it does not want to get hurt, and it searched for a way to relieve the pain, but she does not allow it, and it loves her even more for it, she strengthens it, while others weaken it by things it never meant to make them think, but they do, and they wish that they would stop.

he walked out of the house a sullen look on his face, he headed straight, not caring where he went, only one person on his mind, her, the one he wanted to talk to the most, he had just gotten in a fight, just about a walk he wanted to take.  but this walk was different, he had more motives to be out there, as he walked by her house he stopped and sat at the sidewalk, waiting to see if fate would have her look out the winodw and see him, and she might even walk out and with a beuatiful smile on her face say "Hello", but he waited there 10 minutes, and never did she look out.  so he walked down the block, walking by the huge houses he loved to look at, he wondered why, why his family is in poverty, why do these people live in such big houses? while he is in a small house, with three room instead of four or five, it must have been fate, but why him? he felt that if a car passed by maybe he would get in front of it, and see if it couldn't stop in time.  He stopped and turned to look back down the street at her house, he realized that if fate won't work with him then he would force it.  he made his way slowly to her house, seeing her dad's car in the driveway he feared that her father would tell him to leave, he walked to the door and opened the screen door slowly, the screech loud, he could hear voices inside, he tensed up and knocked on the door, he heard the voices acknowledge that he was at the door as she walked to the door he turned and looked to the sky, she opened the door and he asked quiet and serious, if she wanted to go on a walk, she leaned back to peer into the living room and asked her parents, they said yes, but only for 15 minutes.  they walked away from the house, she kept asking "whats wrong?" and he kept giving answers that were only half true, when really all he wanted to do was turn and kiss her, to show how much he loved her, but he knew he couldn't, he would never be able to talk to her again if he did.  so he kept walking, he told her of his grades, and of the fight over the walk, ande then of the cars, they walked around the block, he looked at her after telling her everything and saw her wiping away the tear.  he looked at her and felt like crying himself, he felt pain go through him, he did not want her to cry, especially for him.  but that changed the night for him, as they reached the corner they stopped, he told her not to worry, he promised her something that he would not break, he said " you should go home now" and she said "where are you going?" he looked behind her and said "that way" and she looked at him and hugged him tightlyhe hugged her back, wishing that they would never have to let go of each other, but she loosened her grip and so did her, he kissed her forehead and said "I love you" and she nodded and started to walk off and he stood there, staring at the ground, and he then he said " I'm serious" he turned to see she was looking at him " I love you" she
